      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/12/35428890/464df75643b85d808ea7457d333c2520_1961070045671290570.png",
                "id": "talent36362",
                "key": "As Water Seeks Equilibrium ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "As Water Seeks Equilibrium "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sourcewater Droplet</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Sourcewater Droplet</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After Neuvillette uses a Normal Attack:</span> Heals the character for 2 HP. After this, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prepare Skill</span>: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Equitable Judgment</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 3 stacks.)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Equitable Judgment</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span><br>(Prepare for 1 turn)<br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>. If this character has at least 6 HP, then this DMG is increased by 1 and this character deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to himself.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/12/35428890/1b23c5ffce1624b3fd3458b534a7f012_4851252319327509051.png",
                "id": "talent63298",
                "key": "O Tears, I Shall Repay",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "O Tears, I Shall Repay"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters on standby, then creates a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sourcewater Droplet</span> with 2 Usages.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Sourcewater Droplet</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After Neuvillette uses a Normal Attack:</span> Heals the character for 2 HP. After this, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prepare Skill</span>: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Equitable Judgment</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 3 stacks.)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Equitable Judgment</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span><br>(Prepare for 1 turn)<br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>. If this character has at least 6 HP, then this DMG is increased by 1 and this character deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to himself.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/12/35428890/83afd6c7a216ef571b8f3868ecdf5b92_3433024857444002371.png",
                "id": "talent77118",
                "key": "O Tides, I Have Returned",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "O Tides, I Have Returned"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_4413049849334196824.png",
                "id": "talent59565",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Prepare Skill</span></strong><br>Some Skills cannot be used directly. Instead, they need to be <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span> over a certain number of turns.<br>When it is a certain player's turn, and this player's active character is currently <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill, this player's turn will be skipped. If the Skill has finished being <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span>, the character will directly use that Skill at this time. (Skills that require <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> cannot activate effects triggered by \"using a Skill\" or \"triggering an Elemental Reaction\" or other such effects.)<br>Only active characters can <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepare</span> Skills, and if an active character who is <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill gets switched off-field, their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparation</span> will be interrupted.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Piercing DMG</span></strong><br>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/13/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3313501052327326354.png",
                "id": "talent98110",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
